---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="uprooted">
  <div class="banner">
    <p><strong>notice:</strong> this project will not release any of its codebase until strict written permission has been granted from the developers of Root.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="page">
    <div class="columns">
      <div class="left">
        <h1>uprooted</h1>
        <p class="sub">a client mod framework for root communications.</p>

        <ul class="features">
          <li>themes</li>
          <li>plugins</li>
          <li>bridge api</li>
        </ul>

        <nav>
          <a href="https://github.com/watchthelight/uprooted">source</a>
          <span class="dot">&middot;</span>
          <span class="dim">gpl-3.0</span>
        </nav>
      </div>

      <div class="right">
        <div class="policy">
          <p>uprooted is currently in <strong>early planning stages</strong>. nothing is available for download yet.</p>
          <p>root's <a href="https://root.gg/terms">terms</a> prohibit reverse engineering and modification of the service. we believe cosmetic client mods can coexist with that policy, but we won't ship anything without explicit approval from root's team.</p>
          <p class="interested">if you're interested, reach out:</p>
          <ul class="contact">
            <li><a href="mailto:admin@watchthelight.org">admin@watchthelight.org</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://discord.com/users/697169405422862417">watchthelight</a> <span class="dim">(discord)</span></li>
            <li><span>Root:watchthelight</span></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="footer dim">not affiliated with root communications.</p>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .banner {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    z-index: 5;
    background: rgba(164, 56, 56, 0.12);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(164, 56, 56, 0.3);
    padding: 10px 24px;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: #d47070;
    text-align: center;
    backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
  }

  .banner strong {
    color: #e08080;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  }

  .page {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    max-width: 860px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 32px;
    height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .columns {
    display: flex;
    gap: 64px;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .left {
    flex: 0 0 auto;
  }

  .right {
    flex: 1;
    padding-top: 4px;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .sub {
    color: var(--dim);
    font-size: 13px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .features {
    list-style: none;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .features li::before {
    content: "- ";
    color: var(--dim);
  }

  nav {
    font-size: 13px;
  }

  .dot {
    color: var(--dim);
    margin: 0 6px;
  }

  .dim {
    color: var(--dim);
  }

  .policy {
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--dim);
    border-left: 2px solid var(--dim);
    padding-left: 16px;
  }

  .policy strong {
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .policy p + p {
    margin-top: 12px;
  }

  .interested {
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .contact {
    list-style: none;
    font-size: 12px;
    margin-top: 8px;
  }

  .contact li {
    padding: 2px 0;
  }

  .contact li::before {
    content: "- ";
    color: var(--dim);
  }

  .footer {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 24px;
    left: 32px;
    font-size: 11px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .columns {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 28px;
    }

    .page {
      padding: 0 20px;
    }

    .footer {
      left: 20px;
    }
  }
</style>
